Carragher: &quot;It's a surprise because it is a derby game, but Klopp has been rotating a lot of late and he's got it spot on.&quot;<br />
<br />
Carragher: &quot;You look at West Brom at home, and no disrespect to them but surely you'd look at that and see that as the game to make changes, you want your best team out for the derby.&quot;

馬馬度沙高：<br />
<br />
Graeme Souness: &quot;I am shocked by that team. This is a derby game, you have to get a win. Everton will be given such a huge lift from that.&quot;

馬馬度沙高：<br />
<br />
Allardyce: &quot;Look at what happened to Chelsea, they lost the game with the same players - Klopp has his squad and he has to use it - he's freshened it up.&quot;
